# ---- NOTE: outputs/ is COMMITTED (not ignored) ----
# The deployed app on Render serves outputs/ directly.
# It contains the pre-built dashboard, maps, analytics, and data files
# that the API reads at runtime (~19 MB total). Without it the app
# won't work unless you rebuild from the raw CSV.
